# Baumholder

[[File:Baumholder - Ort im Hunsrück.png|thumb|Baumholder in the Hunsrück]]
[[File:Baumholder - Ort im Hunsrück.png|250px|Baumholder in the Hunsrück]]

== Town in Rhineland-Palatinate, Germany ==
[[Baumholder]] (German pronunciation: {{IPA|[baʊmˈhɔldɐ]}}) is a [[town]] in the [[Birkenfeld (district)]] [[district]] in [[Rhineland-Palatinate]], [[Germany]], in the [[Westrich]], an historic region that encompasses areas in both [[Germany]] and [[France]]. The town of Baumholder is the administrative seat of the like‑named [[Verbandsgemeinde]], a state‑recognised tourism resort and, according to state planning, a [[Central_place_theory|central place]].

